#: ../../source/api/constituency_count_determiner.rst:2
msgid "ConstituencyCountDeterminer"
msgstr "ConstituencyCountDeterminer"

#: ipres.constituency_count_determiner.ConstituencyCountDeterminer:1 of
msgid "Determines how many constituencies each party is allocated."
msgstr "Bestimmt, wie viele Wahlkreise jeder Partei zugeteilt werden."

#: ipres.constituency_count_determiner.ConstituencyCountDeterminer:3 of
msgid ""
"This is the second of three evaluation steps performed after a finished "
"election. It can be used standalone or as part of "
":class:`~ipres.election_evaluator.ElectionEvaluator`."
msgstr ""
"Dies ist der zweite von drei Auswertungsschritten nach einer "
"abgeschlossenen Wahl. Er kann eigenständig oder als Teil des "
":class:`~ipres.election_evaluator.ElectionEvaluator` verwendet werden."

#: ipres.constituency_count_determiner.ConstituencyCountDeterminer:6 of
msgid ""
"Each party receives approximately half as many constituencies as seats "
"(``seats // 2``). An integer-division correction is applied to ensure the"
" total matches the number of constituencies exactly."
msgstr ""
"Jede Partei erhält ungefähr halb so viele Wahlkreise wie Sitze "
"(``seats // 2``). Eine Ganzzahldivisionskorrektur wird angewendet, um "
"sicherzustellen, dass die Gesamtanzahl exakt der Wahlkreisanzahl entspricht."

#: ipres.constituency_count_determiner.ConstituencyCountDeterminer:10 of
msgid ""
"When the election's ``constituency_representation`` is "
"``GOVERNING_MAJORITY``, only the winning parties are considered; "
"opposition parties receive zero constituencies. The mode is derived "
"automatically from "
"``election.electionConfig.constituency_representation`` inside "
":meth:`run`."
msgstr ""
"Wenn ``constituency_representation`` der Wahl ``GOVERNING_MAJORITY`` ist, "
"werden nur die Gewinnerparteien berücksichtigt; Oppositionsparteien "
"erhalten null Wahlkreise. Der Modus wird innerhalb von :meth:`run` "
"automatisch aus "
"``election.electionConfig.constituency_representation`` abgeleitet."

#: ../../source/api/constituency_count_determiner.rst
msgid "Parameters"
msgstr "Parameter"

#: ipres.constituency_count_determiner.ConstituencyCountDeterminer:17 of
msgid ""
"Strategy for resolving integer-division deficits. When ``None`` "
"(default), the value is inherited from "
"``election.electionConfig.quota_correction_strategy``."
msgstr ""
"Strategie zur Behebung von Ganzzahldivisionsdefiziten. Bei ``None`` "
"(Standard) wird der Wert aus "
"``election.electionConfig.quota_correction_strategy`` übernommen."

#: ipres.constituency_count_determiner.ConstituencyCountDeterminer of
msgid "type"
msgstr ""

#: ipres.constituency_count_determiner.ConstituencyCountDeterminer:21 of
msgid "ipres.election_config.QuotaCorrectionStrategy | None"
msgstr ""

#: ipres.constituency_count_determiner.ConstituencyCountDeterminer:25 of
msgid "Optional callback invoked during quota correction."
msgstr "Optionaler Callback, der während der Quotenkorrektur aufgerufen wird."

#: ipres.constituency_count_determiner.ConstituencyCountDeterminer:27 of
msgid "callable | None"
msgstr ""

#: ipres.constituency_count_determiner.ConstituencyCountDeterminer:31 of
msgid "Pre-built NumPy random generator. Takes precedence over ``seed``."
msgstr "Vorgefertigter NumPy-Zufallsgenerator. Hat Vorrang vor ``seed``."

#: ipres.constituency_count_determiner.ConstituencyCountDeterminer:33 of
msgid "numpy.random._generator.Generator | None"
msgstr ""

#: ipres.constituency_count_determiner.ConstituencyCountDeterminer:37 of
msgid ""
"Seed for the random generator used in quota correction. When ``None`` "
"(default), the value is inherited from ``election.electionConfig.seed``."
msgstr ""
"Seed für den bei der Quotenkorrektur verwendeten Zufallsgenerator. Bei "
"``None`` (Standard) wird der Wert aus ``election.electionConfig.seed`` "
"übernommen."

#: ipres.constituency_count_determiner.ConstituencyCountDeterminer:40 of
msgid "int | None"
msgstr ""

#: ipres.constituency_count_determiner.ConstituencyCountDeterminer.run:1 of
msgid ""
"Calculate constituency counts per party and return a party-to-count "
"mapping."
msgstr ""
"Berechnet die Wahlkreisanzahl pro Partei und gibt eine Zuordnung von "
"Partei zu Anzahl zurück."

#: ipres.constituency_count_determiner.ConstituencyCountDeterminer.run:3 of
msgid "A finished election with a winner."
msgstr "Eine abgeschlossene Wahl mit einem Sieger."

#: ipres.constituency_count_determiner.ConstituencyCountDeterminer.run:4 of
msgid ""
"Seat distribution as returned by "
":class:`~ipres.seat_distributor.SeatDistributor`."
msgstr ""
"Sitzverteilung, wie von "
":class:`~ipres.seat_distributor.SeatDistributor` zurückgegeben."

#: ../../source/api/constituency_count_determiner.rst
msgid "Returns"
msgstr "Rückgabewert"

#: ipres.constituency_count_determiner.ConstituencyCountDeterminer.run:6 of
msgid "Dictionary mapping each party name to its constituency count."
msgstr "Wörterbuch, das jeden Parteinamen seiner Wahlkreisanzahl zuordnet."

#: ../../source/api/constituency_count_determiner.rst
msgid "Return type"
msgstr "Rückgabetyp"
